item.description:
The Boston Demons first intra-club match of 2008 is scheduled for 2pm, Saturday April 26th at Minuteman Technical College in Lexington (more details to follow). To add a little spice to the match-up, the Demons will be split into two squads based on age to create a titanic match-up of the
Demon-Saurasses versus the Diapered Dees (Old vs. Young). All Welcome!

A post-match ANZAC day party will be held at Tommy Doyles Kendall Square later that evening starting 7pm with aussie goodies being raffled off, aussie music and lots of other bonzer stuff going on.
